column5: I was on the Nester falls web site and saw a shocking picture of a fire on the back door of the beach cabin what a shame I hope every one is alright
Is this the picture? It is very dramatic. Hopefully with the rain in the forcast some of these outposts can be saved.
Yup, that's the pic. Hope everything is ok up there! 23 days till we go to lount lake!
